Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,//------------------OPJP-------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.82,0:02:06.40,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}光る　宝石の欠片あつめて
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.46,0:02:13.08,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}両手広げれば青く輝くの
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.13,0:02:19.74,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}やけに眩しくて　瞳閉じたの
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.81,0:02:26.40,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}触れた唇　遠い日の記憶
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.45,0:02:32.90,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}さりげない優しさでも惑わずに
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.95,0:02:40.07,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}運命だって諦めずに変えてみせる
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.43,0:02:47.04,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}翼を広げて　手と手を取り合えば
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.11,0:02:53.75,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}雲の上さえ歩ける気がする
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.81,0:03:00.40,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}{\pos(283,0)\fs10\fsp3}いま
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.81,0:03:00.40,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}あなたのいる現在　耐え難い過去もない
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.45,0:03:07.68,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}無数の光から君を　導く
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,//------------------OPCN-------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.82,0:02:06.40,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}收集着闪光的宝石碎片
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.46,0:02:13.08,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}摊开双手  那辉煌的群青
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.13,0:02:19.74,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}是如此的耀眼  我紧闭双瞳
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.81,0:02:26.40,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}轻抚红唇  遥远的记忆
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.45,0:02:32.90,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}不被那不经意间的温柔所迷惑
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.95,0:02:40.07,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}纵使命中注定  亦从不放弃  将其改变
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.43,0:02:47.04,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}若携君手  振翅翱翔
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.11,0:02:53.75,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}则可漫步云巅
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.81,0:03:00.40,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}在有你的今日里  难熬的过往亦化作烟尘
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.45,0:03:07.68,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}在无数的光辉中指引着你
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,//------------------EDJP-------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.00,0:23:01.38,edjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}雨降るバスでお出かけしても
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.86,0:23:08.35,edjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}あなたは不機嫌なままで歩く
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.82,0:23:15.08,edjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}ご機嫌とると笑顔になるの？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.72,0:23:21.90,edjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}理想の世界を創っていける
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.00,0:23:25.26,edjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}夢の中の出来事
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.63,0:23:29.05,edjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}不満ばかりを　言って
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.10,0:23:31.49,edjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}妄想のロマンス
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.49,0:23:36.16,edjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}私は好きだけど！
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.45,0:23:40.60,edjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}おとぎ話の中でも
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.78,0:23:44.15,edjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}永遠なんてない
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.20,0:23:50.13,edjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}お姫様だってカンカンよ！
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.24,0:23:54.52,edjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}おとぎ話の１ページ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.60,0:23:57.93,edjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}新しいページを
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.98,0:24:05.17,edjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}めくれるのは　（そう）あなた
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,//------------------EDCN-------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.00,0:23:01.38,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}细雨纷纷  纵使乘巴士出行
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.86,0:23:08.35,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}你  仍旧是一脸不悦  埋头行路
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.82,0:23:15.08,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}逢迎你心  便能绽开笑颜？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.72,0:23:21.90,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}理想之乡  即可着手雕塑
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.00,0:23:29.05,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}梦中故事  虽说满腹牢骚
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.10,0:23:36.16,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}但我  却中意于  那妄想的浪漫之中
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.45,0:23:44.15,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}从来就没有什么永恒  即便是在传说里
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.20,0:23:50.13,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}就算是公主  也会生气
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.24,0:23:57.93,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}而那翻开传说的篇章  那崭新的篇章的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.98,0:24:05.17,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}是的  便是你了
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,//------------------INJP-------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.88,0:21:22.06,injp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2}かけがえのない　星たちを見つめ
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.76,0:21:27.35,injp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2}失うことない　輝きでも
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.66,0:21:33.81,injp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2}形あるもの　いつかは壊れる
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.58,0:21:39.16,injp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2}怖がらないで　踏み出そうよ
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.74,0:21:50.17,injp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2}聞こえている　星の言葉
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.56,0:22:07.11,injp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2}さざなみの様に浴びて　僕らは君たちとゆこう
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.30,0:22:15.23,injp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2}これから先のこの未来　輝いている扉開け
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.30,0:22:20.92,injp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2}あなたの胸に飛び込んでゆこう
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.27,0:22:26.92,injp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2}いつまで続くぬくもりを　忘れずにいて永遠に
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.97,0:22:33.42,injp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2}続く未来ずっと
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,//------------------INCN-------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.88,0:21:22.06,incn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2}凝望着  那无可替代的点点繁星
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.76,0:21:27.35,incn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2}纵使是些许的光芒  亦不曾褪去
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.66,0:21:33.81,incn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2}有形之物  终究归于尘土
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.58,0:21:39.16,incn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2}但不必畏惧  请向前迈步
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.74,0:21:50.17,incn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2}我能听见  那群星的絮语
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.56,0:22:07.11,incn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2}萦回耳际  恍若涟漪  前途无尽  但有你我同路
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.30,0:22:15.23,incn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2}远方未来  无限光辉  渐次展开  徐徐大幕
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.30,0:22:20.92,incn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2}我  决定飞入你的胸怀
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.27,0:22:26.92,incn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2}这永不逝去的温暖  我绝不忘却
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.97,0:22:33.42,incn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2}直至明天的旅途
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,//------------------PREV-------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.52,0:00:03.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是…  多重人格吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.41,0:00:09.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对对  这个游戏的主角就有多重人格
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.05,0:00:11.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不是羽田吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.45,0:00:15.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃…不是他
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.42,0:00:16.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.55,0:00:17.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以防万一先问问
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.74,0:00:20.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是「其实我只是做梦睡傻了」这样说的话
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.49,0:00:21.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你真的会相信吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.64,0:00:23.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比较难啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.19,0:00:28.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其实我在这三年里也几次会碰到这样的场景
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.54,0:00:31.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再怎么说  我也是羽田名义上的女朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.10,0:00:35.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,名义上啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.70,0:00:38.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然我也不想说得这么轻率
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.59,0:00:43.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我认为我比起站在那里的某人更能理解羽田
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.60,0:00:45.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「放心吧  我不会对你做什么」
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.13,0:00:47.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「但请你先跟我详细说说」吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.47,0:00:48.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别说得这么讨人厌
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.94,0:00:50.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是想互相帮助
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.25,0:00:51.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,互相帮助？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.89,0:00:53.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  某种程度上说
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.79,0:00:55.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有着跟他相同的境遇
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.66,0:00:57.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,至于这个的来龙去脉
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.80,0:01:00.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就等你说完了我再告诉你
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.80,0:01:04.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我先有个小小的请求
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.06,0:01:07.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(332,323)\fs20}takashi
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.06,0:01:07.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这事请对鹰志君保密
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.10,0:01:09.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么？为什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.56,0:01:13.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他完全不知道他自己里面还有我们这样的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.12,0:01:16.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是让他一下子知道了真相  你知道的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.29,0:01:18.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.44,0:01:19.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我答应你
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.70,0:01:21.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能向天神发誓吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.12,0:01:27.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我对已经不在此世的弟弟发誓
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.79,0:01:30.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就重新自我介绍一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.77,0:01:32.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是千岁鹫介
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.48,0:01:33.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Eagle的鹫
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.48,0:01:35.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,碇矢长介的介  鹫介
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.79,0:01:37.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人称鹫介大湿
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.03,0:01:39.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晚安哟
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.83,0:01:42.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以后请多多指教
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.30,0:01:44.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千岁鹫介
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.43,0:01:47.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Marvelous
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,//------------------TITLE-------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.01,0:03:23.01,title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,心中小鹿乱撞
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,//------------------TXTA-------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.86,0:03:28.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,于是就给说出去了啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.15,0:03:30.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  顺势就…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.97,0:03:32.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少给我扯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.41,0:03:34.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这么几下功夫就…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.49,0:03:37.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们到底为了什么费神至今啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.89,0:03:40.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(337,323)\fs20}takashi
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.89,0:03:40.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为  那好像是鹰志的女朋友嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.41,0:03:42.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那家伙怎么可能有女朋友啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.65,0:03:43.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真过分呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.00,0:03:46.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是本人听见了  可会受打击的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.44,0:03:47.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隼人才是  怎么样啦？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.04,0:03:50.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最近不是有什么干得挺起劲的？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.83,0:03:53.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是不是有心上人了？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.17,0:03:56.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,混蛋  怎么可能
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.01,0:03:58.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有  没有
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.87,0:04:03.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,倒是你  跟那个头上有星星标记的女人怎么样了？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.77,0:04:05.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我跟日和子才没有这样的关系
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.24,0:04:06.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她只是职场上的前辈而已
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.84,0:04:09.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦  那个女人叫日和子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.71,0:04:15.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然这样  无论如何也要把隼人的心上人的名字问出来
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.09,0:04:17.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都说没这号人了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.77,0:04:19.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,告诉我嘛  其实还是有的吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.06,0:04:21.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你当这是修学旅行的夜晚啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.58,0:04:23.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有  别给我转移话题
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.52,0:04:27.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在问你干嘛这么两三下功夫就把我们的秘密说出去了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.34,0:04:31.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毕竟我们也没多少时间了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.74,0:04:37.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(388,323)\fs20}takashi
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.74,0:04:37.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明日香同学也说想帮鹰志君一把
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.87,0:04:39.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.51,0:04:44.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我这边也有不少事要解决呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.30,0:04:46.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,彼此彼此吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.80,0:04:49.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎  关于咱俩
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.20,0:04:49.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是像以前一样
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.85,0:04:51.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,互不干涉
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.86,0:04:54.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(359,323)\fs20}takashi
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.86,0:04:54.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  话说那个鹰志呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.02,0:04:58.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还在格雷塔加尔德那没回来
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.35,0:04:59.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这回去得还真够久的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.12,0:05:00.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么办？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.03,0:05:04.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.37,0:05:07.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,石头剪子
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.87,0:05:08.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,布
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.14,0:05:16.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.53,0:05:18.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千岁先生
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.36,0:05:19.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.56,0:05:21.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天的早饭吃什么呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.27,0:05:23.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请等等
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.70,0:05:29.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小鸠  你还记得我不喜欢吃芦笋啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.00,0:05:33.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,另外咖喱饭  虽然只是昨天的剩饭
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.34,0:05:34.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没关系没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.86,0:05:36.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咖喱放一个晚上会更好吃啦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.39,0:05:38.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.51,0:05:42.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个人怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.07,0:05:43.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(297,323)\fs20}takashi
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.07,0:05:43.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鹰志君吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.10,0:05:47.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是老样子  这次好像去得比较久
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.81,0:05:51.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别担心  我跟隼人君会跟进的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.18,0:05:55.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有千岁先生跟成田先生…吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.95,0:05:56.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,于是呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.93,0:05:58.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…伊丹先生呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.64,0:06:01.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊丹…啊  伽楼罗君吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.84,0:06:03.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他应该不会再出来了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.62,0:06:06.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没什么好在意的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.85,0:06:10.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再怎么说  他这危险的家伙不出来才是造福大众
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.04,0:06:13.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之前也碰到过几次
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.42,0:06:17.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既不是哥哥  也不是那个人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.40,0:06:23.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各种各样的人  不知不觉地就消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.30,0:06:31.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放心吧  小鸠
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.00,0:06:34.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.72,0:06:37.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.77,0:06:39.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.93,0:06:41.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没关系没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.97,0:06:44.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没受伤吧？还好吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.62,0:06:49.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(274,323)\fs20}takashi
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.62,0:06:49.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,演得像鹰志君一样客气一点
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.62,0:06:51.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,客气一点
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.70,0:07:04.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  你也是一个班的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.30,0:07:05.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  你是…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.97,0:07:07.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,午饭吃面包啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.78,0:07:10.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  食堂人太多了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.65,0:07:12.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在路上买的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.57,0:07:14.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了  你也来一个吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.69,0:07:16.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.40,0:07:17.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来如此
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.75,0:07:19.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有别的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.49,0:07:21.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,越来越过瘾了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.94,0:07:23.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎  什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.34,0:07:24.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.10,0:07:30.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.26,0:07:43.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,羽田同学  羽田同学
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.91,0:07:45.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃…谁来着？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.86,0:07:46.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的  在说什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.87,0:07:47.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我啊  我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.89,0:07:49.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小京啊  小京  山科京啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.75,0:07:51.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,山科同学
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.25,0:07:52.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨天真是太棒了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.52,0:07:54.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小京太感激了  太感动了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.54,0:07:56.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感动得全山科都要哭出来了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.03,0:08:01.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没想到羽田同学这么大胆
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.44,0:08:04.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鼓起勇气向你搭话真是做得太对了  不愧是我
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.38,0:08:08.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其实我也是第一次  心里也七上八下的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.92,0:08:11.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,羽田同学对我这么温柔真是太让人高兴了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.47,0:08:12.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这是什么表情
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.26,0:08:13.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不相信吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.00,0:08:13.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真过分呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.04,0:08:16.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可是少女啊  清纯的少女啊  还是处女啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.71,0:08:18.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过现在已经是一个女人了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.90,0:08:21.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(229,323)\fs20}takashi
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.90,0:08:21.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鹰志君到底干了什么了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.46,0:08:23.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光是想起来就已经不能自已
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.59,0:08:25.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,睡也睡不着  睁着眼睛就这么过了一夜
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.12,0:08:28.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蓝色的虽然不行  但是橙色的更加禁止使用啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.81,0:08:32.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过即便这样还是洗不去羽田同学的身影
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.26,0:08:37.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,身体发热  发热  不能自已
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.29,0:08:38.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,于是就做了…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.39,0:08:39.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咽口水
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.41,0:08:41.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…做了什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.92,0:08:44.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,相性占卜
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.08,0:08:46.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厉害  好厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.22,0:08:47.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每一个占卜都棒极了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.00,0:08:49.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管是花  还是星星  还是动物
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.54,0:08:51.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,连龟壳占卜也好极了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.88,0:08:54.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一个人就把这对话持续了这么久
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.56,0:08:55.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的很厉害呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.46,0:08:56.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的可以引以为傲呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.20,0:08:57.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs22}注：miyako=京
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.20,0:08:57.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,羽田君你是made in miyako的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.70,0:09:00.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也很久没露出本性说话了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.26,0:09:01.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也不用就着我…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.35,0:09:07.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,累死了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.29,0:09:13.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(76,323)\fs20}takashi
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.29,0:09:13.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鹰志君也真是的  我还以为他过着本分健全的学生生活
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.68,0:09:14.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没想到除了明日香同学之外
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.70,0:09:16.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有这么多要提防的人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.01,0:09:17.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鹫鹫
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.41,0:09:20.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  什么鹫鹫啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.09,0:09:23.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要是找我有什么事就请叫我的名字
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.51,0:09:24.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鹫之介？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.38,0:09:25.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有之
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.47,0:09:26.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(308,323)\fs20}washi
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.47,0:09:26.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鹫介
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.32,0:09:28.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(308,323)\fs20}washi
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.32,0:09:28.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(376,323)\fs20}shuu
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.32,0:09:28.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,写作鹫读作鹫
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.40,0:09:29.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(285,323)\fs20}shuu
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.40,0:09:29.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鹫之介？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.21,0:09:30.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都说没有之了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.07,0:09:32.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么我的名字是？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.92,0:09:34.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(308,323)\fs20}washi
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.92,0:09:34.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鹫介
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.96,0:09:36.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干嘛又绕回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.10,0:09:37.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎  算了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.08,0:09:39.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢各位捧场
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.96,0:09:44.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(414,323)\fs20}washi
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.96,0:09:44.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说  怎么今天一直都是鹫介啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.21,0:09:46.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有点原因
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.63,0:09:48.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能换羽田君出来吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.64,0:09:50.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(279,323)\fs20}takashi
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.64,0:09:50.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎  这次鹰志君这次不知怎的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.58,0:09:51.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迟迟都不回来
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.02,0:09:54.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,游戏一天只能玩一个小时啊  真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.34,0:09:56.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他什么时候才回来啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.75,0:09:58.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个我也不得而知
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.00,0:10:01.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有话想跟羽田君说
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.81,0:10:04.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(438,323)\fs20}takashi
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.81,0:10:04.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恕我冒昧  请把我当成羽田鹰志吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.54,0:10:08.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呵呵呵  老娘一巴掌扇中你脑袋把你抽晕过去
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.20,0:10:10.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会不会就换回来了呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.55,0:10:13.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇  怎么回事  这个暴力的公主殿下
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.59,0:10:17.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直都是我的回合
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.50,0:10:21.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是这身打扮让人安心
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.61,0:10:24.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了  这个时间的千岁鹫介才是真正的千岁鹫介
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.51,0:10:26.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天也湿湿地上吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.36,0:10:27.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千岁先生  你真吵
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.01,0:10:30.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  借大家一点时间
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.52,0:10:33.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有点事要趁现在说
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.91,0:10:35.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,相信大家也知道
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.24,0:10:37.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,几天后就是平安夜了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.97,0:10:39.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说…店长
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.57,0:10:42.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,男女老少普天同庆的神圣夜晚
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.47,0:10:43.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是对我们饮食业来说
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.96,0:10:45.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这正是决战之夜
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.16,0:10:50.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,于是  我们亚历山大为了吸引更多的客人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.29,0:10:51.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,准备了秘密兵器
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.09,0:10:53.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就是她们
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.78,0:10:56.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本店专属idol unit
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.73,0:10:59.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Alex 2的2位
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.57,0:11:01.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们是Alex 2
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.85,0:11:07.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,英里里  太好了  我们终于能出道了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.92,0:11:09.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别哭嘛  纪奈子
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.37,0:11:11.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种时候偶像更应该微笑着啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.43,0:11:13.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.45,0:11:14.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乖乖别哭  纪奈子妹妹
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.97,0:11:16.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唱两首来听听
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.24,0:11:19.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这帮人真是…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.99,0:11:22.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今后二位将作为本店的形象代表
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.39,0:11:24.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从事本店各种推销活动
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.73,0:11:26.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,平安夜当日
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.75,0:11:28.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还要在店内举行演唱会哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.01,0:11:30.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦  好期待
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.44,0:11:31.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,燃起来了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.94,0:11:33.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,英里里  守护你
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.32,0:11:36.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要忙起来了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.30,0:11:38.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,纪奈子会加油的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.58,0:11:40.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,店长  我有个想法
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.21,0:11:41.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叫我制作人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.74,0:11:43.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,失礼了  制作人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.93,0:11:45.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您忘记了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.14,0:11:47.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本店还有另一颗钻石的原石…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.27,0:11:54.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千岁鹫介
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.49,0:11:55.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要当偶像了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.04,0:11:56.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来如此
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.82,0:11:58.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最近这种的还是有人需要的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.84,0:12:02.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别扔东西啊  被打中的地方好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.31,0:12:05.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回去工作
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.17,0:12:06.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,横peace
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.97,0:12:11.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是受不了了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.68,0:12:12.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这家店子
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.85,0:12:16.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话说  纪奈子小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.12,0:12:17.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不是为了备考  才辞掉工作的么
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.02,0:12:20.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每天跑这儿玩的话  不就没意义了不是？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.03,0:12:22.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀哎呀  别这么说嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.83,0:12:25.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有呢就是  我今天来这儿也是带了这玩意的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.56,0:12:28.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是这样啊  今天发售的么？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.89,0:12:32.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是全文登载了哦  千岁君你写的日和子的书评
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.39,0:12:35.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看  在这儿  就是这儿
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.12,0:12:38.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  我看看  是什么内容呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.60,0:12:40.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果要为这部作品打一个比方的话
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.59,0:12:42.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就恰似在景区步道上闲庭信步一样…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.57,0:12:46.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从淡然的笔触中流露出的诸多情景
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.69,0:12:48.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自然而然  渐次渗出的种种情绪
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.39,0:12:50.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要不要  人家会害羞的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.21,0:12:52.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有人当面朗读自己写的文章什么的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.42,0:12:54.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然作者在这里可能是写得有点不太平易近人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.64,0:12:58.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可总有一天  读者们也应该会理解其文中的深意吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.10,0:12:58.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来如此
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.03,0:13:00.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么样？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.17,0:13:00.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千岁
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.89,0:13:02.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你很会夸人嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.27,0:13:02.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是的说
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.01,0:13:04.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也是这么想的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.14,0:13:05.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢啦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.57,0:13:09.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想人们读了这篇介绍文  应该都会想去读这本书的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.62,0:13:10.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是嘛  就是嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.56,0:13:11.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定要读哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.38,0:13:13.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过实际读完以后  大概是会失望的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.04,0:13:17.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？  为什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.61,0:13:18.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,任谁也不会喜欢的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.83,0:13:21.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让一个隐居山林的老爷子来当主角
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.15,0:13:23.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别这么说嘛  就是这样才好嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.32,0:13:27.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\q2\fsp-1}该怎么说呢  就像是这样  宛如鱿鱼干一样  值得让人反复咀嚼回味
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.86,0:13:29.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,纪奈子你怎么看？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.17,0:13:30.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？  我么？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.22,0:13:34.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…  之前那本我觉得倒是相当不错啦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.11,0:13:37.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过实话实说  这回这本确实是有点不怎么样…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.59,0:13:38.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.13,0:13:42.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其实  就算是让爷爷辈的人来当主角  也不是不行啦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.82,0:13:45.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是描写得一方面是太没有说服力
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.56,0:13:46.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,另一方面  也是因为太年轻
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.79,0:13:48.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以对老人的认识  也就只停留在印象层面
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.98,0:13:51.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那也是没办法的事嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.32,0:13:52.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs22}注：细川玉木是日和子的笔名
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.32,0:13:52.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,细川玉木老师她呀
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.72,0:13:54.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是一个正值青春年少的少女嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.58,0:13:57.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那种年纪轻轻  却又想挑战新境界的创作欲
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.17,0:13:58.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是应该给予肯定的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.83,0:14:01.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果单凭创作欲  书就能卖得动的话  也就没那么多事儿了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.67,0:14:03.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,实际上不是根本卖不动么
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.20,0:14:04.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这第二部作品啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.21,0:14:04.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.88,0:14:06.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要早知是这样  一开始就不该打肿脸充胖子
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.68,0:14:09.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是走老路  写自己拿手的少女恋爱小说不就好了么
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.55,0:14:11.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那样才更受人追捧嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.94,0:14:14.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…  日和…  同学…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.41,0:14:17.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难不成…  全听见了？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.72,0:14:19.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常感谢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.35,0:14:23.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家的感想  我以后执笔的时候  会加以参考的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.35,0:14:24.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢…  谢了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.82,0:14:26.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又装起这副态度了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.65,0:14:28.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「这副态度」是什么意思？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.26,0:14:30.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是这意思
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.14,0:14:35.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎…  我觉得以前的玉木明显更可爱一点嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.83,0:14:40.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我先走了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.49,0:14:41.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,日和子小姐…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.33,0:14:44.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然确实是有一些地方  让人很在意…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.60,0:14:46.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过包括这一些在内
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.42,0:14:50.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我真的很喜欢这部名叫「八十八岁寿辰」的作品
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.42,0:14:50.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs22}注：米字拆开写  即为八十八  因此日本将八十八岁大寿  称作「米寿」
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.63,0:14:58.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说英里同学你啊…  其实也没必要说得那么尖锐嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.87,0:14:59.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什么不好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.11,0:15:02.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对她的话  还是像这样直截了当地挑明了的好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.42,0:15:07.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过英里同学  不管怎么说  你还是读的相当仔细的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.81,0:15:08.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把日和同学她写的书
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,//------------------TXTB-------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.48,0:15:28.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.42,0:15:32.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都这年代了  你们两个居然还没有手机  这也太离谱了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.33,0:15:34.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀  亚衣  冷静  冷静
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.50,0:15:35.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  来了来了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.81,0:15:41.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你搞什么啊  突然这么弄
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.08,0:15:43.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是到头来没意思的话  当心我一拳飞了你哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.63,0:15:44.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.79,0:15:48.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋  又不是找你  我找的是小鸣
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.33,0:15:51.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快来  快来  小鸣
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.93,0:15:54.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这辆  跟小鸣你的自行车  不是挺像的么
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.25,0:15:57.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  确实是红色的没错  但还是有一点不一样
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.79,0:15:59.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎  没找对啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.68,0:16:02.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的自行车  造型稍微有点特别
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.88,0:16:05.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,座位的后面加装了一个靠背
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.54,0:16:07.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  是改装靠背么？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.92,0:16:11.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话说  为什么连你们也集体出动  帮她找自行车啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.00,0:16:14.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？  你说什么啊  这也太过分了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.46,0:16:17.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朋友有难  挺身相助  这不是理所当然的么
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.75,0:16:20.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,另外  也因为我们是这座城市的自警团
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.20,0:16:22.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,柳木原火鸟团的缘故啦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.82,0:16:25.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hi stop  稍等稍等  please
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.09,0:16:26.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Just a time please？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.78,0:16:28.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呀…  好恶心
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.15,0:16:30.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好极
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.20,0:16:34.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是这样的话  也算上我们一份吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.40,0:16:35.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么连你们也来掺上一脚？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.89,0:16:37.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冷静  冷静  长毛君
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.90,0:16:40.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们并不是想来给你们添乱
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.77,0:16:43.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话说  我们这是想来还礼的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.44,0:16:45.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对  对  就是你啦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.48,0:16:46.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.52,0:16:47.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.33,0:16:49.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是你吧没错吧？  成田隼人君
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.59,0:16:52.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把那个Fucking大司教给一拳打飞的  就是你吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.86,0:16:54.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  那事儿啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.93,0:16:59.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他疯成那样  给我们也添了不少麻烦呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.32,0:17:03.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,将天谴降与那已然堕落不堪的妖人的你
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.72,0:17:08.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,方才是将我们引向天堂的传教士
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.68,0:17:10.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哟  成田君超级无敌
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.93,0:17:12.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可以叫你声大哥么
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.13,0:17:13.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哔哩哔哩哔哩
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.66,0:17:15.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这家伙太吵了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.88,0:17:17.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,于是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.34,0:17:21.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就让我们也来帮忙找自行车吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.47,0:17:24.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了回报你的英雄行为
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.70,0:17:26.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,于是大哥你就放一百个心
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.05,0:17:30.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和那边的pretty girl们一起好好乐乐才是真的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.19,0:17:33.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是搞什么名堂啊  他们这些家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.21,0:17:34.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听到了吧  和君
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.95,0:17:36.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这可不能等啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.32,0:17:38.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,必须赶快通知LR他们
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.75,0:17:40.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在就是看那帮人和我们
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.37,0:17:42.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底是哪边先找到小鸣的自行车了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.02,0:17:45.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦也  YFB对R-Wing
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.60,0:17:47.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第二次「世界大战」  就此爆发了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.87,0:17:49.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呀  好燃
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.50,0:17:52.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们两个  先在小春薄饼店那边等着
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.51,0:17:54.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找到了马上联系你们
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.61,0:17:55.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那  就这样了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.50,0:17:56.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,bye bye~
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.96,0:17:58.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走掉了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.44,0:17:59.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之  还是先走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.71,0:18:00.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去小春姐那儿
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.66,0:18:03.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样真的没问题么  皇帝？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.09,0:18:07.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所有成员全部出动  去找小鸣的自行车
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.97,0:18:09.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又有什么不好的？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.41,0:18:11.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正又能够打发时间
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.59,0:18:12.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  是这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.14,0:18:19.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊哈哈  那事情可还真有点大条了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.03,0:18:20.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.76,0:18:21.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.68,0:18:24.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,该说那些家伙是真闲得慌呢  还是…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.18,0:18:25.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这不挺好么
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.57,0:18:28.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比起没事到处乱来  还是正常许多吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.91,0:18:31.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定能找到的  鸣的自行车
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.01,0:18:34.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  谢谢啦  爱丽丝
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.30,0:18:35.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呐  话说你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.45,0:18:36.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.57,0:18:39.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的非那辆自行车不可么？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.93,0:18:42.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就没有去新买一辆的选项么
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.28,0:18:43.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀  那个嘛…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.49,0:18:48.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,严格说来  比起自行车本身  我更想找回篮子里的东西啦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.59,0:18:50.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,里面放了什么特别重要的东西么？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.00,0:18:51.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,寻呼机
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.92,0:18:53.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是大家说的BP机
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.79,0:18:54.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,POCKET BELL…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.25,0:18:56.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有没有搞错…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.23,0:18:57.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.35,0:19:00.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可是从小到大一直在用BP机的死忠哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.86,0:19:02.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃…  该怎么说呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.51,0:19:05.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你可真复古啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.19,0:19:08.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀  我以前也经常靠这玩意的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.74,0:19:11.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过该是时候买部手机了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.00,0:19:13.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事啦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.57,0:19:17.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我没朋友  所以也就没有发短信的对象啦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.36,0:19:18.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,另外…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.60,0:19:22.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那部寻呼机  是妈妈送给我的礼物…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.62,0:19:23.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.05,0:19:29.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我因为家庭原因  妈妈并没有和我住在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.62,0:19:34.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\q2\fsp-1}对于我  除了这寻呼机的号码  我妈妈应该不知道其他的联络手段
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.11,0:19:35.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以…  呵呵
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.62,0:19:38.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.89,0:19:44.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,德拉  一定要找到哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.27,0:19:46.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这孩子的自行车  还有寻呼机
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.13,0:19:46.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.02,0:19:50.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也拜托下看看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.06,0:19:50.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,向我爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.08,0:19:52.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,应该很快就会找到的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.12,0:19:54.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果调动国家的力量的话
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.78,0:19:58.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃…  别搞成国际问题
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.15,0:20:02.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过  敌人是谁  这一点很清楚的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.13,0:20:04.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,应该是大规模犯罪组织的…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.04,0:20:05.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.73,0:20:07.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也曾经见过
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.84,0:20:12.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有一群人把停在吉姆的摊子前面的自行车们全部搬上卡车
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.55,0:20:14.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后统统拖走
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.34,0:20:15.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  那个不是啦  不是啦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.99,0:20:17.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那才不是什么犯罪组织呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.99,0:20:19.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,区政府派来的城管啦  那些人是
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.48,0:20:20.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们这是打着美化环境的旗号
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.85,0:20:23.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没收车站前面乱停乱放的自行车呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.84,0:20:24.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.26,0:20:26.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像偶尔也真在这么搞…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.01,0:20:29.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？  真的么？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.16,0:20:29.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.44,0:20:35.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鸣啊  我想你应该是第一时间就去区政府那边问了的吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.80,0:20:40.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有的啦  我还是头一回听说  区政府还在兼做这事呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.17,0:20:40.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.95,0:20:43.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀  我是归侨子女啦…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.91,0:20:46.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,搬不？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.59,0:20:52.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂  这太阳也太刺眼了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.18,0:20:53.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想干架么  这家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.95,0:20:56.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过  还真是新奇呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.08,0:20:57.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊？  哪儿新奇啦？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.44,0:21:00.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这时间还能和隼人先生你在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.16,0:21:01.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘛  说起来还真是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.57,0:21:04.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  就是这辆！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.29,0:21:06.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是我的自行车啦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.31,0:21:13.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀  话说回来  我们好像忘了联系他们了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.80,0:21:14.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哟  
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.27,0:21:15.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们这群臭乌鸦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.42,0:21:17.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还没放弃么
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.47,0:21:21.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们才是呢  是时候该认输了吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.07,0:21:24.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哼  我们还能再战十年呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.57,0:21:26.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那又怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.65,0:21:28.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,输你个头啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.64,0:21:30.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还在呢！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.99,0:21:32.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  真是太好了…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.46,0:21:35.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的寻呼机…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.22,0:21:35.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是太好了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.16,0:21:36.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.05,0:21:39.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有劳你帮我找了这么长的时间  真是谢谢了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.30,0:21:43.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘛  也没事啦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.86,0:21:44.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.07,0:21:45.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.91,0:21:46.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.44,0:21:49.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没…  没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.41,0:21:56.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…  我说  你等等啊  喂
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.39,0:21:57.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你到底是怎么啦  人家可是很在意的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.87,0:21:59.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是来了什么消息么
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.64,0:22:01.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀  你猜呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.75,0:22:04.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隼人先生
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.76,0:22:06.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到市中心为止  咱们来比一比谁快吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.13,0:22:08.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  我说  你啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.58,0:22:10.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,十一路怎么可能跑得过两轮车嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.84,0:22:13.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可是慢性运动不足啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.56,0:22:16.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隼人先生你也买辆自行车嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.16,0:22:16.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.78,0:22:19.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了  下回要不要大家一起去玩呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.09,0:22:23.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叫上小亚衣和小春姐还有爱丽丝她们
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.13,0:22:24.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  叫你等我啦
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.62,0:22:26.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好…  求你让我喘口气吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.47,0:22:27.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好期待呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.92,0:22:31.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话说  隼人先生你想去哪里呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.33,0:22:33.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀  随便啦  你这家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.64,0:22:34.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看着办吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.82,0:22:39.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊哈哈  心中小鹿乱撞！
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,//------------------NEXT-------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.01,0:24:25.03,next,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(471,0)}{\bord1}次回  请一直当我的粉丝哦
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.64,0:24:12.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗨  大家好  我已经挂啦
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.23,0:24:16.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,DJ秃鹫  今天也在第十八层地狱绝赞死亡中
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.03,0:24:18.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明早就挂了  但还是在说个不停的
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.80,0:24:19.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就只有秃鹫我了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.75,0:24:22.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快向秃鹫老师我发来唁电吧
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.28,0:24:23.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,扫墓
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.23,0:24:24.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你绝对会来的吧？


